snippet.title: "Cuck" Bombs At the Box Office, Amber Heard Hires P.I. To Dig Up Dirt on Depp | HBR News 250
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to HBR News where we talk about the news of the week! This week we look at the Depp/Heard situation, as Amber Heard hires a private investigator in an attempt to dig up dirt on Johnny Depp, news regarding a women who claimed Trump convinced her and her husband to drink fishtank cleaner, a trend on Tik Toom involving women pretending to be domestic abuse victims, and more! Tune in @6pm Eastern to get the scoops!
